info.name: Roblox Old Light Theme (2019)
info.description: ***This style is not updated very often anymore, but I still sometimes work on it. If you have any issues, please let me know.*** This style brings back the old style of Roblox which lasted from early 2019 - late 2019 (strictly that time period, not 2016 or anything like that). It changes every part of the site to look like how it used to. Dark mode is very broken. Someone else is working on a proper 2016 theme built off of this one, it's still a wip but it's looking really nice at the moment, so if you want a true 2016 roblox experience I recommend following its development! Latest screenshot update: October 25th 2020 Some things are missing from the screenshot to save space or protect my privacy, everything is there in the actual style.
info.additionalInfo:
New update! It's been a long while since the last one, so the style's been breaking down a lot over the past couple years. This update should address most of those bugs, sorry it took so long!

---LATEST UPDATE---

+ Future proofed all icons, they should now load immediately and shouldn't break within a couple months anymore.

+ Fixed a lot of graphical annoyances
